[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Exploring Groovy API testing**\n\nI'm considering creating a public API test only, which requires importing groovy.lang.Writable. I need to implement the Writable method to write to a Writer in Java. There’s a potential issue with an overloaded toString method in Groovy that seems the same as Object's toString. I need to determine how a custom Writable would work with StreamingMarkupBuilder and whether the writeTo method is called correctly. Additionally, I should prepare for Groovy initialization failures, catching possible errors like UnsupportedFeature and LinkageError. It looks like I have a lot to figure out!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0db7dcd07156948d016a01b0cb9c14819194f5d2fc46051133\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqAbDR6TXJOh9uLTHTSqw_Y5jZPRvyulJ8CB6qS4EEtbgDOzp4Aaa0Ttgxd2gTITkpY5M6iLihz8dZPN4Bx_r8bce5qoFYfTgmeDRKTUl78kZXs16Aczp4Mlv_qhJXDHcoNo85QPUBkwBd4z59XMNJP9zsC-ikHCjobJ0oeIFaqSka5Lx5FikNHHErS_7-kRZTQsfA6GwgsK-ne3AovtKvLEPXlgR6wEklcGRAFGwQaIn4S6eA2pip1bjPq4wR5Yi0lZpNmv5QOVzySFF_002sQN8Wvn-6WdNCINqlVMj6nIb3Kquy_qjJ624MprWaut-KCCodLNSavYy_HMb056032ITQdB5AxqcMgKtrWZVC5HEPqPknJ-sjuX5l4jTWww-Quj7xMdkRaBkSurg6F0q8eRL7y594yEOk-t5VqSfUFHYvluMvvXesjfSOjOOGh3XGqNu0pRHJd4b1XB5p5NLXKl2aC_xa7EWmMg9Dz-Rz5wnylPASOVXXMFcuYDiIrpqTsMXI3T1DLkuIAmOdKN9FnY2ZF7975gfH4wF2zvK4taEz6XKU9goRAKEa4zqQE0NgMEPQJqirKsawBzccO-Q2agmUsYqlPP6Qq5ibNYt0EF9JNvtMo204XDKt3Ctq26DrVLW65Dw4-gJc6GKRnMnvkcqO-0dETZ4wHTqZbpc9_qC0w12W0mNeADEw96tgdm4DbHr2hUqfzxisPm_n2AqURQj7WjI-DTZOOtzw8hKUvc0smvcvMY3VMuVY2xkLAc9d_iujbT__EpmuhzHS1wFa-FUEj_XdPWKC1j-r0XB32YLqHB2FYNu5Fed1uvBvojVf3A3EZVWDqAJa573Yw55HSxo__k41--ooph_vEuE1H-kjNLzJynhT6UYXk5GVXjerP5Ie9E68VOetjjZABelHWYdLLrDTI46roU_eIkFYGvIujO1x9HGD7Nd0prmaGVsHuF5ruVd1aeOgs55rvtUJLgQhwKwT7PrpjCJDcnd6qqiOEbxqSSURZ2wFhJ7hqVsuK6ENjfCqZxcgyIdC7e5TM6LxOwauheIKgmv-VzHDiLSG3BPUs2C3A0yJTuNV-Uzag02KEVZ7t3wcnbilslMGFjfqk5avUy9hjzQh